---
sidebar_position: 8
title: Retrieve A Bundle Transaction Receipt
sidebar_label: Receipt
description: Retrieve A Bundle Transaction Receipt
---

Returns a transaction receipt made by a bundler.

### Endpoints

```
GET api.stackup.sh/v1/transaction/:transactionHash
```

### Parameters

No parameters.

### Returns

A hash with a data property that contains an array of logs.

### Examples

##### Retrieve a transaction receipt for a UserOperation

```bash
curl --request GET \
  --url https://api.stackup.sh/v1/transaction/0xdbd3d3147e3e0442b14e340cadbe3040b22b1c08801d25ed1a2f7de867160b48  \
  --header 'su-access-key: <api_key>'

```
